<br>
I would propose simply stating our requests without modifying them with conciliatory phraseology. Instead of saying &quot;This is what we want, if balance allows,&quot; say, &quot;This is what we want.&quot; Leave it up to Mythic to determine if it's feasible within the balance structure. We still probably won't get anything, but at least our suggestions won't be immediatley back-burnered. <p><img src="
